{"tid":842744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係香港比人打到豬頭之後, 即使差佬拉到人都係於事無補","createTime":"2018-09-30T14:48:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T16:48:12.000Z","uid":155883,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2dbfdd69df241623c2e525186f25aeca606fdcfa","tid":842744,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:48:34.000Z","msg":"唔明點解隔離POST 會覺得黑警打到人就可以解決件事<br />\n首先我都覺得黑警實拉到人, 但咁又點?<br />\n打人果班個底一早花哂, 可能有部分岩岩坐完出黎<br />\n坐監對佢地黎講只係 SUMMER CAMP<br />\n再坐多次出返黎做地盤, 跟車, 做倉一樣大把人請<br />\n<br />\n比人打果個呢? 片入面條仔比人打到豬頭咁<br />\n入醫院訓返一兩星期, 醫藥費要自己比<br />\n仲有, 你返緊工, 邊個老細會比你CLAIM 兩星期? <br />\n你出院返公司, 全世界都知你講手比人打到傷哂<br />\n背後實笑9你<br />\n當然, 你會話可以民事 claim 返對方<br />\n但過程漫長, 你要睇醫生拎報告, 搵律師上庭 etc..<br />\n到最後claim 得幾十萬  (唔好彤就幾萬), 其實又幫到咩?<br />\n未計心痛, 身痛 同陰影<br />\n<br />\n片中算係打得重, 但比到盡未又係幾星期到兩個月<br />\n香港講手判得有幾重?<br />\n之前有單打到個老豆變植物人都係22個月咋 (行為良好可能年半多啲就出返黎)<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20170911/2_546361_0/-%E6%89%93%E5%88%B0%E8%AE%8A%E6%A4%8D%E7%89%A9%E4%BA%BA-%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E7%89%87-%E5%85%87%E6%89%8B%E8%BC%95%E5%88%A4-%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E8%80%85%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E5%96%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20170911%2F2_546361_0%2F-%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%25A4%258D%25E7%2589%25A9%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E7%2589%2587-%25E5%2585%2587%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25BC%2595%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%2596%258A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25AC&d=2j%2F0E%2FhdxIz%2F47vfqW8je57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=c80b9149\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20170911%2F2_546361_0%2F-%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%25AE%258A%25E6%25A4%258D%25E7%2589%25A9%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E7%2589%2587-%25E5%2585%2587%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25BC%2595%25E5%2588%25A4-%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%2596%258A%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2585%25AC&h=0bc4bc69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20170911/2_546361_0/-%E6%89%93%E5%88%B0%E8%AE%8A%E6%A4%8D%E7%89%A9%E4%BA%BA-%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E7%8F%BE%E5%A0%B4%E7%89%87-%E5%85%87%E6%89%8B%E8%BC%95%E5%88%A4-%E5%8F%97%E5%AE%B3%E8%80%85%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E5%96%8A%E4%B8%8D%E5%85%AC</a><br />\n上面係source<br />\n<br />\n普通打架, 可能推撞或者比人摑一把<br />\n差佬黎到絕對 係「絕對」唔會幫你落案<br />\n一定叫你庭外和解<br />\n因為唔想幫你開file<br />\n你當然可以堅持, 但差佬都覺得你玩野唔抵幫 (講真打架好多時雙方都有責任)<br />\n落口供驗傷磨你一日時間, 再比面色你睇<br />\n仲未計之後要上庭<br />\n通常呢d case都係守口為<br />\n<br />\n如果見紅既比到盡都係留案底, 普通民事爭執好少要坐監<br />\n<br />\n總結, 殺敵一萬, 損兵九千"},{"pid":"357be3a75ba0cb559b890199cf79253a02515ca7","tid":842744,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:01:37.000Z","msg":"明白你嘅心情，有冇更好嘅提議？"},{"pid":"a3730371d09b0916a2b5953a4b5e0b86036f4699","tid":842744,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"357be3a75ba0cb559b890199cf79253a02515ca7","tid":842744,"uid":48286,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T15:01:37.000Z","msg":"明白你嘅心情，有冇更好嘅提議？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T16:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}